high_descs: Stand up turn around move towards the coffee table.
Take the head band from the coffee table.
Turn around move towards the desk lamp.
anns.task_desc: Take the head band from the coffee table and turn on the desk lamp.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to a coffeetable.
Pick up a headband from the coffeetable.
Turn left, get to a corridor in the upper left corner, walk down it until there's a room to your right, get in the room and walk to a place with a desklamp that is in front.
anns.task_desc: Holding a headband, turn on the desklamp.

high_descs: Turn around and head straight, then proceed to turn left towards the coffeetable
Pick up head band from the coffeetable
Turn around and turn left and then head straight towards the desk lamp
anns.task_desc: Examine a head band by the light of a desk lamp
